1. "*Ni* nismo bili sigurni šta da radimo." (We weren't sure what to do.)
2. "*Ni* njegove reči nisu bile od pomoći." (His words weren't of any help.)
3. "*Ni* ona nije bila spremna da prihvati odgovornost." (She wasn't ready to accept responsibility.)
4. "*Ni* početkom prošle godine nisam mislio da će biti tako teško." (I hadn't thought at the beginning of last year that it would be so difficult.)
5. "*Ni* jedan od nas nije imao dovoljno novca." (None of us had enough money.)